(24, 9, NULL, 'uploads/services/1778334051_69ff3963ba663.webp', 'Kundli Matching | Marriage Compatibility Check', 'kundli-matching-marriage-compatibility-check', '<p>Marriage is one of the most important decisions in life ❤️. To ensure a happy and successful married life, it is essential to check compatibility between partners. With <strong>Kundli Matching</strong> by <strong>Astrologer Ankit Shastri Ji</strong>, you can understand the true compatibility, strengths, and challenges in your relationship before marriage 🔮.</p>\r\n<h2>🌟 Accurate Kundli Matching Services</h2>\r\n<p>Astrologer Ankit Shastri Ji uses traditional Vedic astrology methods to match horoscopes (Kundli Milan) and analyze compatibility between partners. This helps in identifying potential issues and ensuring a smooth and harmonious married life.</p>\r\n<h2>💍 What is Checked in Kundli Matching?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Guna Milan (points matching)</li>\r\n<li>Mangal Dosha (Manglik status)</li>\r\n<li>Planetary positions and compatibility</li>\r\n<li>Emotional and mental compatibility</li>\r\n<li>Financial and family life stability</li>\r\n<li>Health and future prospects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>🔮 Benefits of Kundli Matching</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ensures strong and lasting relationship</li>\r\n<li>Reduces chances of conflicts and misunderstandings</li>\r\n<li>Helps in making the right marriage decision</li>\r\n<li>Provides solutions for doshas (if any)</li>\r\n<li>Brings peace, love, and happiness in married life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>🛠️ Remedies for Doshas</h2>\r\n<p>If any dosha or mismatch is found, Astrologer Ankit Shastri Ji provides effective remedies and solutions to minimize negative effects and ensure a successful marriage.</p>\r\n<h2>❤️ Why Choose Ankit Shastri Ji?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>100% accurate and confidential consultation 🤝</li>\r\n<li>Deep knowledge of Vedic astrology</li>\r\n<li>Trusted by thousands of satisfied clients</li>\r\n<li>Online consultation available worldwide 🌍</li>\r\n<li>Personalized guidance for every couple</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>📞 Contact Now for Kundli Matching</h2>\r\n<p>Make the right decision for your future. Get your Kundli matched today and start your married life with confidence and positivity.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Call / WhatsApp:</strong><br>🇮🇳 +91 9915585892<br>🇨🇦 +1 437-776-6381</p>\r\n<h2>✨ Start a Happy Married Life</h2>\r\n<p>With the expert guidance of Astrologer Ankit Shastri Ji, ensure compatibility, avoid future problems, and build a strong and loving relationship 💖</p>', NULL, '2026-04-18 17:44:33', '2026-05-09 18:32:32', 'Kundli Matching | Marriage Compatibility Check', 'Check compatibility before marriage with expert astrologer.', 'kundli matching, horoscope matching'),
