udhiana by Astrologer Ankit Shastri. Baby Kundli preparation, Nakshatra-based naming, horoscope analysis, and future insights for your child\'s growth and success.', 'new born baby astrology in Ludhiana, baby kundli in Ludhiana, baby naming astrologer Ludhiana, nakshatra naming consultation, janam kundli for newborn baby, child horoscope analysis, Astrologer Ankit Shastri'),
(33, 0, NULL, 'uploads/services/1780556018_6a2120f283d53.webp', 'Kaal Sarp Dosha Remedies in Ludhiana – Expert Astrology Guidance for Life Challenges & Spiritual Balance', '-kaal-sarp-dosha-remedies-in-ludhiana-expert-astrology-guidance-for-life-challenges-spiritual-balance', '<p>Many people turn to astrology to better understand recurring obstacles, uncertainties, and challenges they experience in different areas of life. In Vedic astrology, Kaal Sarp Dosha is a commonly discussed planetary combination that some astrologers analyze when evaluating a birth chart.</p>\r\n<p>Astrologer Ankit Shastri offers professional astrology consultations in Ludhiana to help individuals understand their horoscope and gain deeper insights into important planetary influences through traditional Vedic astrology.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">🔮 Understanding Kaal Sarp Dosha</span></p>\r\n<p>According to Vedic astrology, Kaal Sarp Dosha is analyzed based on the placement of planets in relation to Rahu and Ketu within a birth chart.</p>\r\n<p>The interpretation of this planetary combination can vary depending on the overall horoscope, planetary strengths, house placements, and other astrological factors.</p>\r\n<p>A detailed horoscope analysis helps provide a more complete understanding of an individual\'s astrological profile.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"../../service/kundli-reading-in-ludhiana-accurate-horoscope-analysis-personalized-astrology-guidance\">Kundli Reading Services</a></span></p>\r\n<p>A professional horoscope analysis helps evaluate all planetary influences rather than focusing on a single factor.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">📖 Detailed Horoscope Assessment</span></p>\r\n<p>Every Kundli is unique. Therefore, understanding planetary combinations requires a complete analysis of the birth chart.</p>\r\n<p>A consultation may include:</p>\r\n<p>⭐ Birth Chart Analysis</p>\r\n<p>⭐ Planetary Position Evaluation</p>\r\n<p>