(51, 0, NULL, 'uploads/services/1780767797_6a245c352e4ed.webp', 'Best Indian Astrologer in USA: Overseas Education & Study Abroad Astrology Consultation', 'best-indian-astrologer-in-usa-overseas-education-study-abroad-astrology-consultation', '<p>Pursuing higher education abroad is a major milestone for students and families. From selecting the right course and university to planning long-term career goals, every decision plays an important role in shaping the future.</p>\r\n<p>Many students and parents seek personalized guidance while preparing for international education opportunities, university admissions, and career development plans.</p>\r\n<p>Astrologer Ankit Shastri offers professional Overseas Education and Study Abroad Astrology Consultation services for students across the USA through convenient online consultations.</p>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-ac663273-7fff-74f6-988d-741036fd9d88\"><a href=\"../../contact\">&nbsp;Online Astrology Consultation Service</a></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;🌍 Education Planning for Global Opportunities</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Every student has unique strengths, interests, and academic goals.</p>\r\n<p>A personalized consultation may help students explore:</p>\r\n<p>✅ Educational interests</p>\r\n<p>✅ Academic strengths</p>\r\n<p>✅ Career aspirations</p>\r\n<p>✅ Higher education planning</p>\r\n<p>✅ Personal development opportunities</p>\r\n<p>✅ International study goals</p>\r\n<p>✅ Long-term growth planning</p>\r\n<p>Understanding individual strengths can support better educational decision-making.</p>\r\n<p>Many students combine educational consultations with detailed horoscope analysis for future planning.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">📚 Choosing the Right Academic Path</span></p>\r\n<p>Selecting the right educational direction is one of the most important decisions in a student\'s life.</p>\r\n<p>Common consultation topics include:</p>\r\n<p>⭐ Course selection<