(73, 0, NULL, 'uploads/services/1780999596_6a27e5ac408e0.webp', 'Indian Astrologer in New York State for Kundli Matching & Marriage Compatibility Analysis', 'indian-astrologer-in-new-york-state-for-kundli-matching-marriage-compatibility-analysis', '<p>Marriage is one of the most significant life decisions, and many couples seek guidance before taking this important step. Kundli Matching is often used to better understand compatibility, communication styles, shared values, and future expectations.</p>\r\n<p>Across New York State, individuals and families frequently seek astrology consultations while planning engagements, marriages, and long-term relationships.</p>\r\n<p>Astrologer Ankit Shastri offers online Kundli Matching consultations designed to help couples gain deeper insights into relationship compatibility and future planning.</p>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-e994c74c-7fff-cbf9-4505-16442719c796\"><a href=\"../../contact\">Online Astrology Consultation Service</a></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;Understanding Kundli Matching</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Compatibility analysis often focuses on understanding important aspects of a relationship.</p>\r\n<p>A consultation may help individuals explore:</p>\r\n<p>✅ Relationship compatibility</p>\r\n<p>✅ Communication patterns</p>\r\n<p>✅ Shared values</p>\r\n<p>✅ Lifestyle preferences</p>\r\n<p>✅ Future planning</p>\r\n<p>✅ Family expectations</p>\r\n<p>✅ Long-term goals</p>\r\n<p>Many couples seek guidance before making important relationship commitments.</p>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-3b3f023c-7fff-6b0e-9c75-565c6a357e59\"><a href=\"../../service/kundli-matching-marriage-compatibility-check\">Kundli matching service </a></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Marriage Compatibility Analysis</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Understanding compatibility can help couples build stronger relationships.</p>\r\n<p>Common consultation topics include:</p>\r\n<